OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTrain firms set to make new
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpay offer to unions        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Train operating companies are set to   
OL,6, make a new offer to striking rail      
OL,7, workers this week, after receiving a   
OL,8, revised mandate from the government.   
OL,10,FThe Rail Delivery Group (RDG),         
OL,11,Frepresenting the firms, needs          
OL,12,Fgovernment backing for any deal.       
OL,14,FRDG chair Steve Montgomery said he had 
OL,15,Freceived a revised mandate, which would
OL,16,Fbe "used" in talks with the TSSA and   
OL,17,FRMT unions on Thursday.                
OL,19,FDetails could not be shared for        
OL,20,Fconfidentiality reasons, he said.      
